Discworld Creator Help
basic calls

.SH How to show a helpfile to a player
.SP 5 5
Sometimes the best way to answer a player's questions is
simply to send her the helpfile.
This is accomplished by giving the command:
.EP
.SI 5
%^CYAN%^showhelp <player> <helpfile>%^RESET%^.
An example of this would be:
%^CYAN%^showhelp arby liaison%^RESET%^.
.EI
